es Shaar Murray]] (1981). ''Bowie: An Illustrated Record''\n*David Buckley (1999). ''Strange Fascination \u2013 David Bowie: The Definitive Story''\n*Nicholas Pegg (2000). ''The Complete David Bowie''\n\n{{David Bowie}}\n\n{{DEFAULTSORT:Stage (Album)}}\n[[Category:Albums produced by Tony Visconti]]\n[[Category:David Bowie live albums]]\n[[Category:1978 live albums]]\n[[Category:RCA Records live albums]]\n[[Category:Rykodisc live albums]]\n[[Category:Virgin Records live albums]]\n[[Category:EMI Records live albums]]\n[[Category:Albums produced by David Bowie]]\n", "text_old": "{{Use British English|date=January 2014}}\n{{Use dmy dates|date=March 2019}}\n{{Infobox album\n| name       = Stage\n| type       = Live album\n| artist     = [[David Bowie]]\n| cover      = Stage album cover.jpg\n| alt        =\n| released   = 8 September 1978\n| recorded   = 28\u201329 April, 5\u20136 May 1978\n| venue      = {{Collapsible list|title=Various|titlestyle=font-weight:normal;font-size:12px;background:transparent;text-align:left|{{plainlist|\n* [[Wachovia Spectrum|The Spectrum]], [[Philadelphia, Pennsylvania|Philadelphia]]\n* [[Providence Civic Center]], [[Providence, Rhode Island|Providence]]\n* [[Boston Garden]], [[Boston]]\n}}}}\n| studio     =\n| genre      = [[Rock music|Rock]]\n| length     = 73:17 (original LP release) <br> 77:17 (1991 CD version) <br> 85:31 (2005 CD reissue) <br> 94:30 (2017 version)\n| label      = [[RCA Records|RCA]]\n| producer   = {{hlist|David Bowie|[[Tony Visconti]]}}\n| prev_title = [[David Bowie Narrates Prokofiev's Peter and the Wolf]]\n| prev_year  = 1978\n| next_title = [[Lodger (album)|Lodger]]\n| next_year  = 1979\n| misc       = {{Singles\n | name        = Stage\n | type        = Live album\n | single1     = [[Breaking Glass (song)|Breaking Glass]]\" b/w \"[[Art Decade]]\" / \"[[Ziggy Stardust (song)|Ziggy Stardust]]\n | single1date = November 1978\n}}\n}}\n{{Album ratings\n| rev1 = [[AllMusic]]\n| rev1Score =  {{Rating|2|5}}<ref>{{AllMusic |