st\n| all_writing     = \n| collapsed       = no\n| headline        = CD two\n| total_length    = 43:41 (85:31)\n| title1          = Five Years\n| length1         = 3:58\n| title2          = Soul Love\n| length2         = 2:55\n| title3          = Star\n| length3         = 2:25\n| title4          = Hang On to Yourself\n| length4         = 3:21\n| title5          = Ziggy Stardust\n| length5         = 3:37\n| title6          = Art Decade\n| length6         = 3:01\n| title7          = Alabama Song\n| writer7         = Brecht, Weill\n| length7         = 3:55\n| title8          = Station to Station\n| length8         = 8:40\n| title9          = [[Stay (David Bowie song)|Stay]]\n| note9           = Previously unreleased\n| length9         = 7:17\n| title10         = TVC 15\n| length10        = 4:32\n}}\n\n====2017 rerelease track listing====\n\nIn 2017, the album was included, in two versions, in the ''[[A New Career in a New Town (1977\u20131982)]]'' [[box set]] released by Parlophone.  One version contained the original mix and the same list and ordering of tracks that had appeared on the original vinyl album; the other was a new version of the album, based on the 2005 edition but including two previously unreleased songs from the concerts.<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.davidbowie.com/news/new-career-new-town-1977-1982-57146 |title=A New Career in a New Town (1977\u20131982) |website=David Bowie |date=12 July 2016 |accessdate=21 February 2018 |url-status=dead |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20170713014523/http://www.davidbowie.com/news/new-career-new-town-1977-1982-57146 |archivedate=13 July 2017  }}</ref> The latter was also released separately, in 2-CD and 3-LP formats, in 2018.<ref>{{cite web |author=Paul Sinclair |date=19 January 2018 |url=http://www.superdeluxeedition.com/news/david-bowie-remastered-berlin-albums-available-separately-next-month |title=David Bowie / Remastered \u2018Berlin\u2019 albums available separately next month |website=Super Deluxe Edition |accessdate=21 February 2018}}</ref>\n\n{{tracklist\n| all_writing     = \n| collapsed       = no\n| headline        =Side one\n| total_length    = 17:37\n| title1 = Warszawa\n| length1 = 6:53\n| title2= \"Heroes\"\n| length2 = 6:19\n| title3 = What in the World\n| length3 = 4:25\n|extra_column=|note1=|writer1=Bowie, Eno|extra1=|note2=|writer2=Bowie, Eno|extra2=|note3=|writer3=|extra3=|note4=|writer4=|extra4=}}{{tracklist\n| all_writing     = \n| collapsed       = no\n| headline        =Side two\n| total_length    = 16:13\n| title4 = Be My Wife\n| length4 = 2:49\n| title5 = [[The Jean Genie]]\n| length5 = 6:17\n| title6 = Blackout\n| length6 = 4:00\n| title7 = Sense of Doubt\n| length7 = 3:07\n|extra_column=|note4=|writer4=|extra4=|note5=Previously unreleased|writer5=|extra5=|note7=|writer7=|extra7=|note8=|writer8=|extra8=}}\n{{tracklist\n| all_writing     = \n| collapsed       = no\n| headline        =Side three\n| total_length    = 15:21\n| title8 = Speed of Life\n| length8 = 2:40\n| title9 = Breaking Glass\n| length9 = 3:22\n| title10= Beauty and the Beast\n| length10= 5:06\n| title11= Fame\n| length11= 4:13\n|extra_column=|note9=|writer9=Bowie, Davis, Murray|extra9=|note10=|writer10=|extra10=|note11=|writer11=Bowie, Alomar, Lennon|extra11=|note12=|writer12=|extra12=|note13=|writer13=|extra13=}}\n{{tracklist\n| all_writing     = \n| collapsed       = no\n| headline        =Side four\n| total_length    = 17:43\n| title12 = Five Years\n| length12 = 3:57\n| title13 = Soul Love\n| length13 = 2:56\n| title14 = Star\n| length14 = 2:28\n| title15 = Hang On to Yourself\n| length15 = 3:22\n| title16 = Ziggy Stardust\n| length16 = 3:30\n| title17 = [[Suffragette City]]\n| length17 = 3:58\n|extra_column=|note14=|writer14=Bowie, Eno|extra14=|note15=|writer15=|extra15=|note16=|writer16=|extra16=|note17=Previously unreleased|writer17=|extra17=}}\n{{tracklist\n| all_writing     = \n| collapsed       = no\n| headline        =Side five\n| total_length    = 15:39\n| title18